1
00:00:44,039 --> 00:00:46,960
The oil lamp burns through the Yin-Yang Divide

2
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:49,799
The Lamp Keeper stands at the Gates of Hell

3
00:00:50,119 --> 00:00:50,880
You two kids

4
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:52,119
Remember this well

5
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:53,719
We must never let the Eternal Lamp

6
00:00:53,719 --> 00:00:55,759
of the Bone-Keeping Temple go out

7
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:58,960
What if the wind blows it out?

8
00:01:03,399 --> 00:01:04,239
If the lamp dies

9
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:05,840
I die

10
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,439
Little lady

11
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:24,920
Out here in the dead of night

12
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,120
Widowhood must be so lonely

13
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:26,640
How about

14
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,040
you keep us brothers company?

15
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:28,920
Come on

16
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,000
Come here

17
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:31,359
Lay her down

18
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:34,599
Hold her down!

19
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,480
Pin her down

20
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:37,000
No!

21
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,239
Stop!

22
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:39,760
Haven't had a piece like this in ages

23
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,359
Let me go!

24
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,439
Feels good

25
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:47,959
Feels great!

26
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,959
Lord Beile

27
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,280
I'm begging you

28
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,840
Please let my father go in

29
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,560
Sure

30
00:01:59,079 --> 00:02:01,000
But if your father goes in

31
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,120
where do we go?

32
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,680
The rain's too heavy

33
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,480
I'm begging you

34
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,239
Lord Beile

35
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,359
Please, I beg you

36
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,159
Here

37
00:02:09,159 --> 00:02:10,879
Hold an umbrella for your father

38
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,639
Wouldn't want him getting soaked

39
00:02:26,639 --> 00:02:27,560
This is outrageous

40
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,520
Exactly

41
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,439
Bullying

42
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:30,560
us living folk is one thing

43
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,479
But now he's bullying the dead too

44
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,479
That man

45
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:34,319
will get what he deserves sooner or later

46
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,039
Keep your voice down

47
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,639
His brother-in-law is the Mayor

48
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,039
Cross him and you'll...

49
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:41,000
Move

50
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:42,479
You all

51
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,520
Father!

52
00:02:53,759 --> 00:02:54,439
Lord Beile

53
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:56,400
You just don't know what's good for you, huh?

54
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,919
Smash the coffin open!

55
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:01,360
No!

56
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:02,439
I'm begging you

57
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,879
Lord Beile, I beg you

58
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:06,759
Smash it!

59
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,800
It's alive!

60
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,439
Little brother

61
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,360
Don't eat me

62
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,159
Don't eat me

63
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,560
Little brother

64
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,120
Master

65
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:52,199
A Daoist Priest is here to see you

66
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:54,639
Daoist Priest

67
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,560
How did it go?

68
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,719
Child's play

69
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:09,439
He's awake

70
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:10,560
He's awake

71
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,120
It's a Jiangshi

72
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,919
A Jiangshi!

73
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:18,399
Serves you right

74
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,720
You turned the Bone-Keeping Temple
into a chaotic mess

75
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:22,519
You're getting what you deserve

76
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,959
The Mayor is mistaken

77
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,000
A Jiangshi

78
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:30,639
forms when Resentful Energy gathers
in the corpse's throat

79
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,560
festering and refusing to disperse

80
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:34,480
To become a Jiangshi

81
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:37,120
the corpse must be buried in

82
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:39,079
the Land of Converging Nine Yins

83
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,360
for fifty years

84
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:41,759
Becoming a Jiangshi

85
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,319
is no easy feat

86
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:47,600
Why would I lie to you?

87
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,959
Everyone saw it

88
00:04:54,279 --> 00:04:55,519
In that case

89
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,000
Tonight

90
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,839
I'll confront him myself

91
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,040
Daoist Priest

92
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,800
He's right inside that room

93
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:08,079
You

94
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,439
Get over here

95
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:09,439
Tie him up

96
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,279
Brother-in-law is calling you

97
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,680
Hurry up

98
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,519
He's calling you

99
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,600
Why does it have to be me?

100
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,319
You caused this trouble

101
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:16,199
You expect me to go?

102
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,040
I refuse to believe it

103
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,560
Even immortals fear a puff of smoke

104
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,319
Today, I'll see your
body and soul obliterated!

105
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,160
Men!

106
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,360
Lady Fox Immortal is here

107
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,120
Who dares be insolent?

108
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:04,800
Hurry, hurry!

109
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,639
Don't let him escape

110
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,199
Catch him

111
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:07,399
Hurry, catch him!

112
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,720
Lady Fox Immortal

113
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:09,240
You fools!

114
00:07:10,319 --> 00:07:11,560
Hurry and catch him!

115
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:13,560
Lady Fox Immortal

116
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,120
Daoist Priest

117
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:15,199
He got away

118
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,319
Good thing he got away

119
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,319
Thank you

120
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:40,959
Your name is Ruling, right?

121
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,160
Why did you save me?

122
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:48,680
Then why did you save me?

123
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,000
The dying lamp won't go out

124
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,480
Boundary between Yin and Yang

125
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,480
The Lamp Keeper remains

126
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,000
The vow of the living

127
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,639
Such heavy yin energy

128
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,879
Is this sung for the dead to hear?

129
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:10,799
Or sung by the dead for the living?

130
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:49,720
Five Thunders, Five Thunders

131
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,399
Heavenly thunder follows

132
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,080
Thunder in my palm

133
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:51,840
Strike ghosts and banish evil
